-- Samsung Chairman Lee to Promote His Son to President, MoneyToday Reports
-- B y   B o m i   L i m
-- 2010-11-17T05:19:41Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-17/samsung-chairman-lee-to-promote-his-son-to-president-moneytoday-reports.html
Samsung Electronics Co. plans to
promote Lee Jae Yong to the position of president, MoneyToday
reported, citing his father, Chairman Lee Kun Hee. Lee Jae Yong
is currently an executive vice president of the company,
according to the Korean-language report.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Bomi Lim in Seoul at 
